The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 US-Russia title clash

Paris: Defending champions Italy brushed aside China 5-0 to set up a Fed Cup semi-final showdown at home in mid-July against France. 

The French crushed Japan 5-0 in Limoges. 

Russia whitewashed Spain in Moscow on Sunday to advance to a final-four clash with the United States. 

The US posted a 5-0 victory over Belgium. Svetlana Kuznetsova fired Russia into the final four with a 6-3, 4-6, 6-0 win over Anabel Medina Garrigues. (AFP) 




